rent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; color: rgb(44, 44, 44); width: calc(100% - 112px); font-family: &quot;Roboto Regular&quot; !important;\">Dự &aacute;n KĐT Y&ecirc;n Trung, X&atilde; Thụy H&ograve;a, Y&ecirc;n Phong, Bắc Ninh</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"re__list-standard-1line--md cs_cursor\" id=\"css_cs_pointer\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 14px 0px; line-height: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); border-left: none; border-image: initial; display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: flex-start; position: relative; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Medium&quot; !important;\"><span class=\"title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; color: rgb(44, 44, 44); width: 112px;\">Mặt tiền:</span><span class=\"value\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; color: rgb(44, 44, 44); width: calc(100% - 112px); font-family: &quot;Roboto Regular&quot; !important;\">25 m</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"re__list-standard-1line--md\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px 16px; padding: 14px 0px; line-height: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); border-left: none; border-image: initial; display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: flex-start; position: relative; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Roboto Medium&quot; !important;\"><span class=\"title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; ma